 1301   static const mxArray *emlrt_marshallOut(const char * u)
 1302   {
 1303     const mxArray *y;
 1304     const mxArray *m0;
 1305     y = NULL;
 1306     m0 = mxCreateString(u);
 1307     emlrtAssign(&y, m0);
 1308     return y;
 1309   }
 1310   
 1311   static const mxArray *b_emlrt_marshallOut(uint32_T u)
 1312   {
 1313     const mxArray *y;
 1314     const mxArray *m1;
 1315     y = NULL;
 1316     m1 = mxCreateNumericMatrix(1, 1, mxUINT32_CLASS, mxREAL);
 1317     *(uint32_T *)mxGetData(m1) = u;
 1318     emlrtAssign(&y, m1);
 1319     return y;
 1320   }
